Pantron raced down the hillside into the mountains. He saw the base come into view. Thanks to the signal from magmatron pantron found it easily. Soon he arrived at the base. He looked around ans saw no one. He walked in and saw magmatron. He was obviously going to reprogram the cat bot into a destron. Maybe he could convince magmatron to make him a tm2 panther. He greeted Bobertron he had chande much. But he was as noble as ever. Thats what he liked about him. Even thought it would eventualy get him killed.
